<h1> Letter from Guppy - 1-18-20 </h1>
<a href="https://pelechjohn.github.io/Correspondence-of-John/home.html"> ‚Üê index </a>
<br>
<p> 
I find your treatment of our mutual friend, Sir William Topaz McGonagall deeply disturbing. Instead of providing Christian fellowship and a place of lodging for our distressed friend, you have allowed him to linger in the streets. Utterly shameful. While his heretical teetotal beliefs are genuinely disturbing, you must not leave a friend in the cold. 
</p>
<p>
Best regards,
</p>
<p>
Koselitz 
</p>
